Hexo Blog Template123456789101112131415--- # 文件开始title: Hexo Blog Template # 标题，注意不要有标点符号date: 2019-04-14 23:00:52 # 格式一致tags: # 自定义标签，可根据需求自行增加删改，建议尽量保持跟网站上已有的命名标准一致（此处不区分大小写）- tag1 - tag2categories: blog # 目前仅支持两种模式：blog, event。blog是指research blog类型的文章，event是指event类型的活动文章---内容简介 # 这里的内容会放到文章的简介界面，不建议放入过多内容## Title 2 // 文章一律从markdown的二级标题开始，其余与markdown语法一致（建议使用基本的markdown语法，高级功能可能不支持）### Title 3#### Title 4","categories":[{"name":"blog","slug":"blog","permalink":"https://pris-nlp.github.io/categories/blog/"}],"tags":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","permalink":"https://pris-nlp.github.io/tags/hexo/"}]},{"title":"test","slug":"blog_2","date":"2019-04-14T15:00:52.000Z","updated":"2019-04-19T12:34:47.328Z","comments":true,"path":"2019/04/14/blog_2/","link":"","permalink":"https://pris-nlp.github.io/2019/04/14/blog_2/","excerpt":"","text":"hello world","categories":[{"name":"event","slug":"event","permalink":"https://pris-nlp.github.io/categories/event/"}],"tags":[{"name":"tag1","slug":"tag1","permalink":"https://pris-nlp.github.io/tags/tag1/"},{"name":"tag2","slug":"tag2","permalink":"https://pris-nlp.github.io/tags/tag2/"}]},{"title":"test","slug":"blog_4","date":"2019-04-14T15:00:52.000Z","updated":"2019-04-21T13:47:56.670Z","comments":true,"path":"2019/04/14/blog_4/","link":"","permalink":"https://pris-nlp.github.io/2019/04/14/blog_4/","excerpt":"","text":"hello world","categories":[{"name":"blog","slug":"blog","permalink":"https://pris-nlp.github.io/categories/blog/"}],"tags":[{"name":"tag1","slug":"tag1","permalink":"https://pris-nlp.github.io/tags/tag1/"},{"name":"tag2","slug":"tag2","permalink":"https://pris-nlp.github.io/tags/tag2/"}]},{"title":"test","slug":"blog_3","date":"2019-04-14T15:00:52.000Z","updated":"2019-04-19T12:34:53.610Z","comments":true,"path":"2019/04/14/blog_3/","link":"","permalink":"https://pris-nlp.github.io/2019/04/14/blog_3/","excerpt":"","text":"hello world","categories":[{"name":"event","slug":"event","permalink":"https://pris-nlp.github.